The liturgical calendar and scripture readings represented in
lectionary_data.json are traditional works of the Armenian Church
(Տօնացոյց / Ճաշոց) and are not claimed as original authorship. The
readings table was distilled and cross-year validated during development
using sacredtradition.am (https://www.sacredtradition.am/) as a
ground-truth reference; that source is not contacted at runtime and its
raw cache is not distributed with this repository.
